main event: The report contains multiple photographs of unidentified flying objects (UFOs) over residential areas and rural locations in Ontario, Canada on September 20, 1967.
interesting points: The UFOs appear to be dark, disc-shaped objects or blurry silhouettes of aerial vehicles.
The photographs were part of a Project Blue Book document from the Foreign Technology Division of the AFSC (Air Force Systems Command).
The UFOs are depicted hovering over neighborhoods, fields, and forests in the images.
The photographs vary in quality, with some being blurry or indistinct.
No human figures are visible in the photographs, suggesting the UFOs were photographed without witnesses present.
sighted object: dark, disc-shaped objects or blurry silhouettes of aerial vehicles
photographs: yes, the report contains 10 photographs of UFOs
